## There is no GitHub Actions CI that builds the DMG

The only workflow under `.github/workflows/` is **React Doctor** — it scans React code on Ubuntu. It does not build or publish a DMG.

```1:31:.github/workflows/react-doctor.yml
# React Doctor — finds security, performance, correctness, accessibility,
# bundle-size, and architecture issues in React codebases.
...
jobs:
  react-doctor:
    runs-on: ubuntu-latest
```

The DMG pipeline is **local + scripted**, not CI. That’s explicit in `up.md`:

> "No CI complexity required immediately" and "Build the macOS DMG locally on an Apple Silicon Mac."

