## Risks to plan for

| Risk | Mitigation |
|------|------------|
| `node-pty` native build on Windows | Build only on `windows-latest` |
| Unsigned EXE SmartScreen warnings | Document like Mac unsigned DMG flow |
| Same version, two upload paths | Shared tag `v<version>`, separate manifests |
| Accidentally changing Mac `dist` | Add `dist:win`; leave `dist` as Mac-only |
| Launcher updater on Windows | Phase 2: accept `.exe` in manifest + installer flow (today is DMG/macOS only) |

